parts.str: NOTE: If you are filling this in on behalf of someone else, please answer all the questions as if you are that person
Have you had any of the following symptoms since your last visit (or in the past weeks, if this is your first visit)?
On your last visit, you reported that you were still ill. Are the symptoms you report today part of the same bout of illness?
In the 14 days before your symptoms started, did you travel to an area at risk for new coronavirus infection?
In which area(s) at risk of infection did you go within 14 days before the onset of your symptoms?

In the 14 days before your symptoms started, have you been in contact with someone for whom tests have confirmed that they have Covid-19?
Do you live in the same household as that person?

In the 14 days before your symptoms started, have you been in close contact with someone presenting symptoms of COVID-19? (Symptoms of COVID-19 include: fever or chills, cough, sore throat, shortness of breath, sore muscles and headache.)
Do you live in the same household as that person?
NOTE: To save you time, we have filled in the information you gave us previously about your illness. Please check that it is still correct, and make any changes if necessary.
When did the first symptoms appear?
Did your symptoms develop suddenly over a few hours?
Did your fever develop suddenly over a few hours?
What was your highest temperature measured?
Because of your symptoms, did you VISIT (see face to face) any medical services?
Hospital accident & emergency department / out of hours service
No, but I have an appointment scheduled
How soon after your symptoms appeared did you first VISIT a medical service?
Hospital accident & emergency department/out of hours service
Because of your symptoms, did you call [write the COVID-19 emergency line of your country]?
Because of your symptoms, did you call [write the general emergency line of your country]?
Because of your symptoms, did you contact via TELEPHONE or INTERNET any of medical services?
GP - spoke to doctor or nurse
How soon after your symptoms appeared did you first contact a medical service via TELEPHONE or INTERNET?
GP - spoke to doctor or nurse
Did you take medication for these symptoms (tick all that apply)?
Pain killers (e.g. paracetamol including Lemsip, ibuprofen, aspirin, Calpol, etc)
How long after the beginning of your symptoms did you start taking antiviral medication?
Because of your symptoms, were you hospitalized?
Did you change your daily routine because of your illness?
Yes, but I did not take time off work/school
Yes, I took time off work/school
Other (e.g. I wouldn’t usually be at work/school today anyway)
How long have you been off work/school?
Because of your symptoms, did you wear a mask (surgical mask sold in pharmacies)?
No, I would have liked but could not find any
Because of your symptoms, have you taken or strengthened one or more of the following measures?
Cough or sneeze into your elbow
Stop greeting by hugging and/or kissing on both cheeks
Limit your use of public transport
Avoid gatherings (going to the theater, cinema, stadium, supermarket, etc.)
Telework or increase your number of telework days
Avoid travel outside your own country or region
Have your food-shopping delivered by a store or a friend/family member
Avoid being in contact with people over 65 years or with a chronic disease
Avoid being in contact with children
What do you think is causing your symptoms?
For which reason(s) do you think you have this disease? (Select all the relevant answers)
My doctor told me I have this disease
I had a laboratory confirmation that I have this disease
I had direct contact with a laboratory confirmed case
I had close contact with someone for whom a doctor diagnosed this disease
I was in close contact with someone presenting symptoms of this disease
I was at an event/location with a confirmed case
I think I have this disease
Have you informed people who have been in close contact with you about your suspicion of COVID-19 infection?
Since the beginning of COVID-19 lockdown measures, do you carry out a professional activity? (Select all the relevant answers)
Yes, I work outside from home
No, I have a leave of absence to take care of my kid(s)
No, I have a sick leave (because of Covid-19)
No, I have another situation (retired, job-seeker, student, house-wife/husband, other sick-leave, partial unemployment, forced leave…)
How many days a week do you work outside from home?
Over recent days, at which frequency did you go out of home to buy products, on average?
I do not go out of home anymore
Over recent days, at which frequency did you go out of home to get fresh air or exercise (outside your home, balcony, garden, private courtyard), on average?
I do not go out of home anymore
Over the course of yesterday, how many people (outside your household) did you approach at a distance lower than 1 meter?
If lockdown measures were lifted up, but collective childcare/schools/university were closed, what would be your situation? (Select all the relevant answers)
I would work outside from home
I would have a leave of absence to take care of my kid(s)
I would have a sick leave (because of Covid-19)
I would be in another situation (retired, job-seeker, student, house-wife/husband, other sick-leave, partial unemployment, forced leave…)
How many days a week would you work outside from home?
If lockdown measures were extended (that is to say, continued beyond the date announced by the government), do you think you would follow the recommendations with as much rigour as you do now?
On a scale of 0 to 100, where 0 means the WORST health you can imagine and 100 means the BEST health you can imagine, how good or bad is your health today?
NOTE: If you have been vaccinated since completing the registration questionnaire please go back to update this new information.
